WEBVTT

01:33:38.358 --> 01:33:39.899
Err... to meet Jose!

01:33:39.983 --> 01:33:41.191
-Yes, Jose...
-But...

01:33:41.233 --> 01:33:42.649
doesn't the doctor usually call me?

01:33:42.649 --> 01:33:44.149
She couldn't get through to you.

01:33:44.191 --> 01:33:45.483
So she called me instead.

01:33:45.524 --> 01:33:47.941
If you don't believe me,
just ask the doctor! What is this?

01:33:49.024 --> 01:33:50.149
What did you find?

01:33:50.191 --> 01:33:51.233
It's an older model Jeep.
